Package sticmacpiernov.spreadsheet.panel

Provides classes for the window panel content.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Criteria
    This class represents the list of criteria displayed on the user interface.
    Criterion
    This class represents a criterion selectable in the graphical user interface.
    Limit
    This class contains a text box used to specify the number of results to display.
    ResultsTable
    This class is a container for the results table.
    Sort
    This class displays component on the user interface for choosing the sorting column and the order.
